ğŸ‘©ğŸ»â€ğŸ’» Code : 

import spidev
import time

spi = spidev.SpiDev(0,0)
spi.open(0,0)
msg = 0xAA
spi.max_speed_hz = 115200

while 1:
   spi.writebytes([0x4,0x06])
   # resp = spi.xfer2(0xAA)
   y = spi.readbytes(0xAA)
   print(y)
   time.sleep(0.5)

----------

To Save this -> ctrl + s
To Exit from the Program ->  ctrl + x
To Run File  ->  python3 filename


â–ªï¸Upload arduino code  from arduino app to Arduino kit - connection with raspberry Pi  with jumper wire

Arduino pin no is for..
11 connection ->  mosi
12 - miso
13 - clock

Raspberry pi..
19 pin for - mosi
21 - miso
23 - clock

Jumper connection wire
11 - 19
12 - 21
13 - 23

â–ªï¸For run 
In Raspberry pi Terminal 
Python3 filename.py ,

â–ªï¸In Arduino Tools - goto Port - Select com6 or 4 
For checking.

